earning their degradation representations from the facial portions, which can\nbe used to significantly improve the quality of non-facial areas. The source\ncode is available at https://github.com/csxmli2016/ReDegNet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2022 08:09:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2022 03:09:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-17"}
