 lie at a distance of about 8.62 $\\times$\n10$^{14}$ cm from the central engine of BL Lac.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2022 10:14:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-21"}
