 mirror experiencing a\nrelativistic trajectory, that is, a mirror producing the dynamical Casimir\neffect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2022 14:47:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-04"}
